window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Magnus and Kaitlyn have new commitments, adventures, and dangers, taking them from 1929 New York City to 1887 Montana, 1904 Paris, and to a war for their kingdom in the 24th century.<br> <br> Magnus has challenges that await. Kaitlyn has loved ones to protect. In the middle of the turmoil, they have promises they must keep.<br> <br> It all begins with a simple request: Magnus, please come....<br> <br> This is book 17 of the Kaitlyn and the Highlander series, a contemporary romance with a dash of history and a bit of sci-fi. The series must begin with book one.</p> <p>If you love mysterious heroes with desperate hearts and romantic thoughts, heroines with courage who are also very ordinary disasters, and love stories that encompass all time, then you’ll love this suspenseful series.</p>"; 
